value.string: To Format the input file by updating the valid Horison IDs
1. Unique email ids to be extracted and stored in a list.
2.Incrementation of Horison ID number for each unique email id for all the rows in the template file.

3. For one specific partner, a logic to extract the last 4 digits of the SSN Number, also splitting the alphanumeric number and appending the alphabet with the SSN Number(Alphabet + SSN Number)  and then updating the Horison ID in Column U for all the rows in the partner file.
4. Updating the new incremented Horison ID in Column U for all the rows in the partner file for the remaining 9 partners
5. In case of failure while Loading the file/entering to a field, ERROR flag will be raised and BOT may be stopped.
